00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:18,208
I have the authority to cease
Wei Yen's communication equipment.

258
00:21:18,291 --> 00:21:20,666
What are you doing?
You can't just barge in!

259
00:21:21,375 --> 00:21:22,875
Mrs. Wei, I'll see you later.

260
00:21:22,958 --> 00:21:25,083
- You're leaving?
- Yeah. I'll be back tomorrow.

261
00:21:29,875 --> 00:21:32,250
- You can't just take his stuff.
- Is this his phone?

262
00:21:37,958 --> 00:21:39,583
Are you the attending physician?

263
00:21:39,666 --> 00:21:41,500
I'm not. Why?

264
00:21:41,583 --> 00:21:43,708
Okay. Please sign in, then.

265
00:21:43,791 --> 00:21:45,291
I need to register?

266
00:21:45,375 --> 00:21:48,625
Only the attending physician
and family are allowed in.

267
00:21:48,708 --> 00:21:50,333
- Should I call it in?
- All good. Don't worry.

268
00:21:50,416 --> 00:21:51,625
- I'll keep going. Thanks.
- Okay.

269
00:21:57,958 --> 00:21:59,208
<i>You can go.</i>

270
00:21:59,291 --> 00:22:01,791
Sir, didn't Mr. Jen tell us
to wait for him to get back?

271
00:22:01,875 --> 00:22:03,375
Give him his stuff now.

272
00:22:03,458 --> 00:22:05,333
- Sir?
- Stay out of it.

273
00:22:07,625 --> 00:22:08,833
You can go now.

274
00:22:10,250 --> 00:22:11,291
Go on.

275
00:22:59,833 --> 00:23:02,750
<i>Oh, shit. That's bad. Guys…</i>

276
00:23:02,833 --> 00:23:04,625
- <i>Oh, fuck.</i>
- <i>What do we do?</i>

277
00:23:04,708 --> 00:23:06,208
<i>Should we help?</i>

278
00:23:07,916 --> 00:23:09,458
- <i>Let's go.</i>
- <i>Should we call the police?</i>

279
00:23:09,541 --> 00:23:11,208
- <i>Come on. Let's go.</i>
- <i>Let's get out of here.</i>

280
00:23:54,666 --> 00:23:56,041
VIDEO UPLOAD

281
00:23:57,583 --> 00:23:58,750
UPLOADING FILE

282
00:24:03,958 --> 00:24:05,666
I know. It's your doing!

283
00:24:06,250 --> 00:24:07,750
Your video is on the internet!

284
00:24:14,250 --> 00:24:18,291
Why is this video
different from the one online?

285
00:24:25,166 --> 00:24:27,166
This is what I found on your computer.

286
00:24:31,125 --> 00:24:33,750
This is the version circulating online.

287
00:24:34,333 --> 00:24:36,166
So, why do you have it?

288
00:24:36,875 --> 00:24:41,000
Kuo Ta-fu, you've already
caused two deaths.

289
00:24:41,083 --> 00:24:43,916
You realize you could serve
two life terms for this.

290
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,041
I suggest you cooperate.

291
00:24:46,791 --> 00:24:48,250
You gave it to me.

292
00:24:49,125 --> 00:24:50,333
Just now.

293
00:24:52,416 --> 00:24:54,541
So, you didn't upload it?

294
00:24:55,416 --> 00:24:57,625
You're a fucking cop. Investigate.

295
00:25:04,875 --> 00:25:07,583
I'm not the only one who wants them dead.

296
00:26:06,291 --> 00:26:09,583
Hey. A-Li. Good you're here.
I was informed that…

297
00:26:09,666 --> 00:26:11,250
Sir…

298
00:26:11,916 --> 00:26:13,833
- Don't make this hard.
- What is this?

299
00:26:14,666 --> 00:26:16,416
A-Hua, what's all this?

300
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:18,250
Cooperate.

301
00:26:19,916 --> 00:26:21,291
Why are you filming?!

302
00:26:21,375 --> 00:26:23,625
- I'm a cop! Why are you filming?
- Chen-wei!

303
00:26:27,250 --> 00:26:29,125
Li Hsin-ping, what's the gun for?

304
00:26:30,333 --> 00:26:32,708
What the fuck are you all doing?! Huh?

305
00:26:34,208 --> 00:26:37,000
The deceased's name was Chao Kuo-an.

306
00:26:37,083 --> 00:26:40,166
He was also Chen-wei's informant.

307
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,250
Mr. Ho?

308
00:26:46,583 --> 00:26:48,458
Bet you didn't see this coming.

309
00:26:52,375 --> 00:26:53,750
You wanna kill me?

310
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,708
<i>If I didn't sabotage the heart monitor,</i>

311
00:26:58,791 --> 00:27:00,333
<i>you really would've killed him.</i>

312
00:27:05,291 --> 00:27:09,583
Look here, guys.
I'd say we found the real killer.

313
00:27:13,083 --> 00:27:15,250
<i>Yo Tzu used</i>
<i>Baba's account to do a live stream.</i>

314
00:27:15,333 --> 00:27:16,916
<i>He really wanted to kill Wei Yen.</i>

315
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,708
<i>It's on Witch Baba's live stream?</i>

316
00:27:18,791 --> 00:27:20,250
<i>That's insane.</i>

317
00:27:26,291 --> 00:27:28,250
<i>Taipei High Technology</i>
<i>Crime Investigation.</i>

318
00:27:28,333 --> 00:27:30,666
- <i>Chen-wei.</i>
- <i>Yo Tzu! Wei Yen! Cool!</i>

319
00:27:31,791 --> 00:27:34,000
- <i>New memes are coming.</i>
- <i>Got you.</i>

320
00:27:36,500 --> 00:27:37,625
WHO WILL SAVE WEI YEN?

321
00:27:37,708 --> 00:27:39,500
MURDERER!

322
00:27:39,583 --> 00:27:41,333
<i>I waited all night for this.</i>

323
00:27:42,916 --> 00:27:45,416
- <i>Did anyone call the police?</i>
- <i>He's a cop himself.</i>

324
00:27:45,500 --> 00:27:48,000
MURDERER!

325
00:27:48,083 --> 00:27:49,375
EGG WATER RIVER STUDIO

326
00:27:49,458 --> 00:27:51,833
- We got him!
- It's him?!

327
00:27:56,666 --> 00:27:58,041
So scary.

328
00:27:58,125 --> 00:28:00,791
Well, look what we've found.

329
00:28:00,875 --> 00:28:03,833
Huh? Caught red-handed.

330
00:28:03,916 --> 00:28:06,125
Not just a cop, but a squad leader.

331
00:28:06,208 --> 00:28:07,875
Let's see if you can cover this one up.

332
00:28:07,958 --> 00:28:09,166
Kid, back away.

333
00:28:09,916 --> 00:28:12,541
Asshole. Disgraceful.

334
00:28:12,625 --> 00:28:14,958
HE MUST TAKE RESPONSIBILITY
FOR THOSE PEOPLE'S LIVES!

335
00:28:16,458 --> 00:28:18,208
<i>Put the gun down!</i>

336
00:28:19,375 --> 00:28:21,666
Wait a sec.

337
00:28:22,416 --> 00:28:23,500
ATTEMPTING TO RECONNECT

338
00:28:26,041 --> 00:28:27,208
Why is it gone? Hey!

339
00:28:27,291 --> 00:28:28,333
It's down!

340
00:28:28,416 --> 00:28:30,958
- Is it a problem with the connection?
- Must be on his end.

341
00:28:31,541 --> 00:28:32,583
Yo Tzu?

342
00:28:33,291 --> 00:28:34,833
Is the live stream up anywhere else?

343
00:28:34,916 --> 00:28:36,791
- WHERE IS THIS?
- I'M A NURSE AT THE NURSE STATION

344
00:28:36,875 --> 00:28:38,250
Why are you filming?

345
00:28:38,333 --> 00:28:39,666
THIS NURSE IS ON THE SCENE

346
00:28:41,125 --> 00:28:42,208
Someone posted a link.

347
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,208
Let's get it up.

348
00:28:47,375 --> 00:28:49,000
IT WAS DISCONNECTED JUST NOW!

349
00:28:49,083 --> 00:28:50,458
<i>Put the gun down!</i>

350
00:28:50,541 --> 00:28:51,916
<i>Don't.</i>

351
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,125
<i>Chen-wei!</i>

352
00:28:54,916 --> 00:28:56,625
<i>Back off! Guns down!</i>

353
00:28:56,708 --> 00:28:58,041
Hey! Hey! Hey!

354
00:28:58,125 --> 00:28:59,291
- Bro!
- What the actual hell?!

355
00:29:00,333 --> 00:29:01,583
This is horrifying.

356
00:29:01,666 --> 00:29:04,625
I know. This is all a setup.

357
00:29:04,708 --> 00:29:07,625
I'm the Investigation Unit
Squad Leader. Guns down!

358
00:29:07,708 --> 00:29:08,875
Chen-wei.

359
00:29:10,041 --> 00:29:13,125
Give it up. You're an influencer now.

360
00:29:15,041 --> 00:29:17,916
Okay. We'll cut the act.

361
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,041
Guns down!

362
00:29:19,708 --> 00:29:21,583
Back off! Guns down!

363
00:29:21,666 --> 00:29:24,291
Guns down! Guns down!

364
00:29:24,375 --> 00:29:25,666
Fuck, don't you get it?!

365
00:29:27,666 --> 00:29:28,791
Guns down!

366
00:29:34,708 --> 00:29:37,083
Guns on the ground. Guns on the ground!

367
00:29:41,166 --> 00:29:42,000
Now go!

368
00:29:47,333 --> 00:29:48,500
Back off.

369
00:29:48,583 --> 00:29:51,000
Fucking back off! Didn't I tell you?!

370
00:29:52,375 --> 00:29:54,750
FILMER, BE MORE RESPONSIBLE

371
00:29:57,541 --> 00:29:59,333
CAN ALSO PRAY
TO GIVE THE POLICE MORE POWER

372
00:29:59,416 --> 00:30:01,291
YOU FEEL AT EASE
TO LEAVE IT TO THE POLICE?

373
00:30:01,375 --> 00:30:02,375
Stay back.

374
00:30:02,958 --> 00:30:04,958
- Chen-wei…
- Go away! Fuck off!

375
00:30:05,041 --> 00:30:07,791
Just calm down. Okay?

376
00:30:07,875 --> 00:30:09,791
Gonna shoot, are you? I dare you to do it.

377
00:30:09,875 --> 00:30:11,625
Press the button.

378
00:30:15,166 --> 00:30:16,791
You wouldn't dare shoot me.

379
00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:20,625
- Wait. Don't shoot me.
- I'm a police officer! You wouldn't dare!

380
00:30:23,833 --> 00:30:24,666
Don't.

381
00:30:26,750 --> 00:30:28,416
- Yo Tzu.
- Yeah?

382
00:30:29,041 --> 00:30:30,041
You're ugly.

383
00:30:30,625 --> 00:30:32,166
Are you serious?

384
00:30:32,250 --> 00:30:35,333
<i>It's not ugly. You're ugly. Look.</i>

385
00:30:35,833 --> 00:30:36,750
What's Up Yo! Yo!

386
00:30:36,833 --> 00:30:38,041
Yo, yo!

387
00:30:38,125 --> 00:30:40,083
Yo, yo! Yo!

388
00:30:44,708 --> 00:30:45,666
What's up?

389
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:48,041
- What is this?
- Can we not do that?

390
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:50,000
What's up?

391
00:30:51,166 --> 00:30:52,416
Yo…

392
00:31:05,458 --> 00:31:06,875
BABA ISN'T THERE?

393
00:31:06,958 --> 00:31:08,625
WEI YEN IS ON THE SCENE!

394
00:31:08,708 --> 00:31:11,000
THIS IS MORE NERVOUS
THAN MY WIFE GIVING BIRTH

395
00:31:40,375 --> 00:31:43,083
Fuck. You scared me to death.

396
00:31:54,458 --> 00:31:56,333
- Bro, are you okay?
- I'm okay.

397
00:32:03,458 --> 00:32:04,750
YO TZU IS SAFE

398
00:32:04,833 --> 00:32:09,208
<i>Guys, it's me.</i>
<i>I'm safe. Officer Jen saved me.</i>

399
00:32:11,291 --> 00:32:13,000
That's my dad.

400
00:32:13,083 --> 00:32:14,375
That was so scary.

401
00:32:14,458 --> 00:32:16,500
Oh, I was so worried.

402
00:32:27,208 --> 00:32:28,125
<i>Oh my gosh.</i>

403
00:32:28,208 --> 00:32:29,875
<i>Ho Chen-wei was also arrested.</i>

404
00:32:29,958 --> 00:32:32,041
<i>Looking forward to</i>
<i>the next episode of Wei Fa Yen.</i>

405
00:32:32,125 --> 00:32:34,083
<i>Wa Zai and Kao Pi can rest in peace now.</i>

406
00:32:34,166 --> 00:32:36,166
<i>- Wei Yen is amazing.</i>
- <i>R.I.P.</i>

407
00:32:36,250 --> 00:32:38,000
<i>Yo Tzu and Wei Yen, get some rest.</i>

408
00:32:38,083 --> 00:32:39,291
<i>Looking forward to tomorrow.</i>

409
00:32:39,375 --> 00:32:40,625
- <i>Good night.</i>
- <i>Bye.</i>

410
00:32:46,291 --> 00:32:49,500
Welcome to What's Up Yo! Yo!

411
00:32:49,583 --> 00:32:52,625
The place we're at today
looks like a home.

412
00:32:52,708 --> 00:32:55,166
Can you guess whose house?

413
00:32:55,250 --> 00:32:57,375
Any predictions?

414
00:32:57,458 --> 00:33:00,500
Today's guest… is a big shot.

415
00:33:00,583 --> 00:33:03,375
Witch Baba!

416
00:33:03,458 --> 00:33:06,458
Hello, everyone. I'm Witch Baba!

417
00:33:06,541 --> 00:33:10,333
All right. This…
is a long-awaited unboxing video

418
00:33:10,416 --> 00:33:12,208
in Witch Baba's prediction room.

419
00:33:12,291 --> 00:33:14,041
Hey, by the way…

420
00:33:14,125 --> 00:33:15,833
Can you not wear that mask?
It's terrifying.

421
00:33:15,916 --> 00:33:18,708
I'm sorry. It's a bit nerve-racking.

422
00:33:18,791 --> 00:33:21,708
Why so nervous?
You have a million followers.

423
00:33:21,791 --> 00:33:24,125
Before we do the unboxing,

424
00:33:24,208 --> 00:33:25,625
how about a prediction?

425
00:33:25,708 --> 00:33:28,333
Predict this!

426
00:33:28,416 --> 00:33:30,583
How's my injury healing?

427
00:33:30,666 --> 00:33:32,750
Okay, then. As usual…

428
00:33:32,833 --> 00:33:35,958
First, What's Up Yo! Yo!,
please draw a card for us.

429
00:33:36,041 --> 00:33:38,208
- This one.
- Reversed London Big Ben.

430
00:33:38,291 --> 00:33:40,958
It signifies that time is on a standstill.

431
00:33:41,041 --> 00:33:43,375
So, that means
your recovery time is almost done.

432
00:33:44,583 --> 00:33:45,875
Am I right?

433
00:33:45,958 --> 00:33:47,958
- Hey! Oh!
- See, it doesn't hurt! Hah!

434
00:33:48,041 --> 00:33:48,916
- Well…
- It's all better.

435
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:50,500
Let's see if you're right.

436
00:33:51,666 --> 00:33:53,500
Ladies and gentlemen…

437
00:33:53,583 --> 00:33:55,375
- Hey, wait. Where's your injury?
- Dun dun!

438
00:33:55,458 --> 00:33:58,291
Let me demonstrate
Yo Tzu's strong recovery.

439
00:33:58,375 --> 00:33:59,916
- That's impossible.
- Hmm?

440
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,791
- Do you know why?
- Why?

441
00:34:01,875 --> 00:34:03,041
It's actually this arm.

442
00:34:03,125 --> 00:34:05,125
Oh my God. You're so lame!

443
00:34:05,208 --> 00:34:06,750
All right. Seriously, though…

444
00:34:06,833 --> 00:34:09,916
We actually have
some important stuff to talk about.

445
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:14,000
Recently, we experienced
something horrible.

446
00:34:14,083 --> 00:34:15,291
That's right.

447
00:34:15,375 --> 00:34:17,208
And…

448
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:24,041
we both personally… witnessed everything.

449
00:34:25,375 --> 00:34:29,625
We apologize, again, to everyone affected.

450
00:34:29,708 --> 00:34:31,791
- We're sorry.
- We're sorry.

451
00:34:33,583 --> 00:34:37,833
We will continue to help the police
with their investigation.

452
00:34:37,916 --> 00:34:41,125
I also hope everyone is well.

453
00:34:42,458 --> 00:34:47,125
That's right. We've talked
about a very… heavy topic,

454
00:34:47,208 --> 00:34:48,416
so let's brighten it up.

455
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,958
My good friend, Chen Yu-chieh…

456
00:34:52,125 --> 00:34:54,333
…will be having
her first solo headline concert soon.

457
00:34:54,416 --> 00:34:58,125
That's right. Next week, on December 7th…

458
00:34:58,208 --> 00:34:59,625
…9:30 p.m.

459
00:34:59,708 --> 00:35:00,791
See you there.

460
00:35:00,875 --> 00:35:02,291
<i>You must come!</i>

461
00:35:05,916 --> 00:35:07,166
Chia-jen.

462
00:35:14,250 --> 00:35:17,416
Why are you still frowning?
This business is all over.

463
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:25,458
Kuo Ta-fu took cyanide.
He was planning to die, and so…

464
00:35:25,541 --> 00:35:28,000
It was in his late wife's bracelet.

465
00:35:28,083 --> 00:35:31,083
The hospital gave him
dispensation to wear it.

466
00:35:32,041 --> 00:35:33,041
Also,

467
00:35:34,333 --> 00:35:35,583
Lin Ting-yu has been sentenced.

468
00:35:35,666 --> 00:35:36,875
Hmm.

469
00:35:37,583 --> 00:35:39,416
For endangering and damaging a vehicle,

470
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:43,541
the judge gave him
and Wei Meng-yen… 60 days.

471
00:35:45,666 --> 00:35:47,208
Wei Meng-yen, he's…

472
00:35:47,291 --> 00:35:49,458
- Discharged.
- Ah.

473
00:35:49,541 --> 00:35:50,958
They won't prosecute.

474
00:35:51,541 --> 00:35:53,208
Seems you're off the hook.

475
00:35:58,333 --> 00:35:59,500
Tell me…

476
00:35:59,583 --> 00:36:02,500
- Uh…
- You're asking about Chen-wei?

477
00:36:02,583 --> 00:36:03,833
Not really.

478
00:36:03,916 --> 00:36:08,083
Your bullet. It went straight
through his right clavicle.

479
00:36:09,041 --> 00:36:12,083
His life's not in danger.
I guess you're fortunate.

480
00:36:12,166 --> 00:36:14,750
Hey, I calculated well, and I aimed well.

481
00:36:14,833 --> 00:36:16,583
You aimed well? Oh, yeah.

482
00:36:16,666 --> 00:36:20,750
You put a bullet in him vindictively,
trouble would be heading your way.

483
00:36:20,833 --> 00:36:22,291
All right, then. I'm off.

484
00:36:22,375 --> 00:36:24,000
You go. I need a smoke.

485
00:36:24,083 --> 00:36:26,083
Here. You want one?

486
00:36:26,166 --> 00:36:27,500
Forget it. You quit.

487
00:36:27,583 --> 00:36:30,000
Don't smoke. Hurry. You go. Off you go.

488
00:36:30,083 --> 00:36:30,916
Go on.

489
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,541
You take it easy, now. It's bad for you.

490
00:36:35,875 --> 00:36:37,666
Concerned, are you?

491
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:40,083
I guess you go online all the time now.

492
00:36:40,166 --> 00:36:42,166
That's where my daughter is.

493
00:37:36,250 --> 00:37:39,583
DJ CHEN YU-CHIEH'S SOLO CONCERT

494
00:38:52,875 --> 00:38:54,208
Yu-chieh!

495
00:38:56,208 --> 00:38:57,375
Yu-chieh!

496
00:38:59,625 --> 00:39:03,333
This next song is for my dad.
